<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureBuffer.SetPerformanceHints" Title="SetPerformanceHints method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureBuffer">ITextureBuffer</PageRef> ->
    SetPerformanceHints
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>SetPerformanceHints</TypeRef> method provides hints to the renderer about how this texture buffer will be read and written.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void SetPerformanceHints(PerformanceHint performanceHintCpu, PerformanceHint performanceHintGpu);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="PerformanceHint" Name="performanceHintCpu">
          The hint describing how the CPU is expected to read from or write to the resource.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="PerformanceHint" Name="performanceHintGpu">
          The hint describing how the GPU is expected to read from or write to the resource.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureBuffer">ITextureBuffer</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
